com.bitplan.expr

Class PrimrecexprBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.bitplan.expr.PrimrecexprBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PrimrecexprListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class PrimrecexprBaseListener
extends Object
implements PrimrecexprListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of PrimrecexprListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
